snippet.title: Unpacking - Official Mobile Reveal Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Unpacking will be available on phone and tablet in 2023. Watch the trailer to see the reveal, and take another look at this zen puzzle game about the familiar experience of pulling possessions out of boxes and fitting them into a new home.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
